data.description: Shelby Floor Plan. Quality Bussell built home!!Room off of family room can be office/formal dining rm. or 4th bedroom. This beautiful home with open great room plan includes granite counter tops, custom knotty alder cabinets, hardwood floors, walk-in pantry in kitchen. Master suite has walk-in closet with dual vanity in bathroom! Also includes Brick/stone front,  3-car garage & 10x10 concrete patio. All Bussell built homes include energy efficient green features; R40 & R15 high density insulation, low E argon gas windows, 16 SEER A/C unit & 95%+ efficiency heat.
